revision.text: Possibly: Του μεγαλου Ιπποκρατουσ παντων των ιατρων κορυφαιου τα ευρισκομενα. = Magni Hippocratis medicorum omnium facile principis, Opera omnia quae extant, in VIII. sectiones ex Erotiani mente distributa..., by Hippocrates. (Francofurti [Frankfurt am Main] : In officina Danielis ac Dauidis Aubriorum, & Clementis Scleichij, Anno M.D.C.XXIV. [1624]). http://library.st-andrews.ac.uk/record=b1433595~S1
